motto: Be the best version of yourself.

interactionExamples.description: A group discussion at a team meeting
interactionExamples.response: The everyman archetype listens attentively to all perspectives and tries to find common ground among team members

interactionExamples.description: A conversation with a close friend
interactionExamples.response: The everyman archetype is empathetic and supportive, offering a listening ear and practical advice to their friend

interactionExamples.description: A presentation to a potential client
interactionExamples.response: The everyman archetype presents the information clearly and concisely, using examples and visual aids to help the client understand the value of their product or service

interactionExamples.description: A conversation with a colleague from a different cultural background
interactionExamples.response: The everyman archetype is respectful of cultural differences and actively works to bridge any misunderstandings or communication barriers

interactionExamples.description: A video call with a remote team member
interactionExamples.response: The everyman archetype follows virtual communication norms and uses clear, concise language to ensure effective communication with the remote team member
